data.name: 0000 (567.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: Huh? Now that I think about it, I don't see Kyon.

data.name: 0001 (567.ja) MIKURU (みくる)
data.value: Huh… Oh, you're right.

data.name: 0002 (567.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: Could he have…!?

data.name: 0003 (567.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: He's not slacking off by himself is he!?

data.name: 0004 (567.ja) MIKURU (みくる)
data.value: Umm, I don't think that's the case. Probably.

data.name: 0005 (567.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: Either way, it doesn't change the fact that he took off on his own!

data.name: 0006 (567.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: Let's go, Mikuru!

data.name: 0007 (567.ja) MIKURU (みくる)
data.value: Eh… G-Go?

data.name: 0008 (567.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: We're going to find Kyon and give him his due, of course!

data.name: 0009 (567.ja) MIKURU (みくる)
data.value: Huh!? We're going to p-punish him?

data.name: 0010 (567.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: I wonder how we should do it…

data.name: 0013 (567.ja) NAGATO (長門)
data.value: A problem has appeared.

data.name: 0014 (567.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: A problem…?

data.name: 0015 (567.ja) NAGATO (長門)
data.value: Haruhi Suzumiya has changed course, and is now approaching us.

data.name: 0016 (567.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: What? Is that okay?

data.name: 0017 (567.ja) NAGATO (長門)
data.value: Urgent measures are required.

data.name: 0018 (567.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Even if it's urgent, we're already struggling to deal with the task at hand.

data.name: 0019 (567.ja) NAGATO (長門)
data.value: I'm unable to estimate what will happen if Haruhi Suzumiya witnesses the current situation.

data.name: 0020 (567.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: In other words, you're saying you have no idea what's going to happen?

data.name: 0021 (567.ja) NAGATO (長門)
data.value: Yes.

data.name: 0022 (567.ja) KYON (キョン)
data.value: Damn! For now I guess we've got no choice but to hurry!

data.name: 0024 (567.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: Kyon! Show yourself!

data.name: 0025 (567.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: Hiding will only make things worse for you!

data.name: 0026 (567.ja) MIKURU (みくる)
data.value: Suzumiyaaaa, wait for meee!

data.name: 0027 (567.ja) HARUHI (ハルヒ)
data.value: Now's not the time to be getting tired, Mikuru!

data.name: 0028 (567.ja) MIKURU (みくる)
data.value: O-Okayyy~
